    "content": "[Intro]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-5---5---5---5---5---5---5--------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[Verse 1]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|---0--2----2--3--2--2--0----0----------0--2--2------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-3-----------------------------3----3---------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nSome Say Love It Is A River That Drowns The Tender Reed[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----0--2----2--3--2--2--0---0----------0--2--2------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-3-----------------------------3----3---------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nSome Say Love It Is A Razor That Leaves Your Soul To Bleed[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-2--3--5----5--5--5--5------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|------------------------5----7--8--7--5--3--0-------------------------------------------|\r\nA|-----------------------------------------------3----------------------------------------|\r\nE|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nSome Say Love It Is A Hunger An Endless Aching Need[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----0--2----2--3--2--2--0----0--------0-------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-3------------------------------3--3-----3--3-------------------------------------------|\r\nA|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nI Say Love It Is A Flower And You It\u2019s Only Seed[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[Verse 2]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----0--2----2--3--2--2--0----0--0-------0--2--2-----------------------------------------|\r\nD|-3---------------------------------3----------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nIt\u2019s The Heart Afraid Of Breaking That Never Learns To Dance[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----0--2---2--3--2--2--0----0--0-------0--2--2-----------------------------------------|\r\nD|-3--------------------------------3-----------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nIt\u2019s The Dream Afraid Of Breaking That Never Takes The Chance[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-2--3--5----5--5--5--5------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|------------------------5----7--8----7--5--3--0-----------------------------------------|\r\nA|-------------------------------------------------3--------------------------------------|\r\nE|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nIt\u2019s The One Who Won\u2019t Be Taken Who Cannot Seem To Give[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----0--2----2--3--2--2--0----0--0-------0-----------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-3---------------------------------3-------3--3-----------------------------------------|\r\nA|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nAnd The Soul Afraid Of Dying That Never Learns To Live[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[Verse 3]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----0--2----2--3--2--2--0----0--0----------0--2--2--------------------------------------|\r\nD|-3---------------------------------3----3-----------------------------------------------|\r\nA|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nWhen The Nights Have Been Too Lonely And The Road Has Been Too Long[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----0--2----2--3--2--2--0----0--0--0-------0--2--2--------------------------------------|\r\nD|-3------------------------------------3-------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nAnd You Think That Love Is Only For The Lucky And The Strong[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-7--8--10--10----10--10--10--5----7--7--8----7--5--3--0---------------------------------|\r\nA|---------------------------------------------------------3------------------------------|\r\nE|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nJust Remember In The Winter Far Beneath The Bitter Snow[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|--------7----7--8--7--7--5----5--5--3----3--5----3--3-----------------------------------|\r\nA|-8--10----------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nLies The Seed That With The Sun\u2019s Love In The Spring Becomes The Rose[/tab]",
